OL,3,CIncome tax cut proposed in Guernsey
OL,4,Calongside introduction of GST
OL,6,FGuernsey's top political committee are
OL,7,Fproposing sweeping tax changes to be
OL,8,Fdebated later this year.
OL,10,FThe Policy and Resources Committee
OL,11,F(P&R) has published a policy letter
OL,12,Ftoday (Monday 12 January) asking the
OL,13,FAssembly to agree to measures to
OL,14,Freform the island's tax system.
OL,16,FThe main change is the cut to income
OL,17,Ftax, which currently stands at 20%.
OL,18,FUnder the proposals, that would be cut
OL,19,Fto 15% for those earning #32,400 or
OL,20,Fless a year.
