OL,4,Calongside introduction of GST
OL,6,FHowever, this comes with the
OL,7,Fproposition to introduce a 5% tax on
OL,8,Fmost goods and services, including
OL,9,Ffood.
OL,11,FIn the previous government, Guernsey
OL,12,Fpoliticians agreed to introduce a
OL,13,FGoods and Services Tax (GST) by 2027,
OL,14,Fbut it has been hotly debated for
OL,15,Fyears, having been voted down three
OL,16,Ftimes in previous political terms.
