OL,3,CIncome tax cut proposed in Guernsey
OL,4,Calongside introduction of GST
OL,6,FP&R have stated that the
OL,7,Frecommendation to approve GST follows
OL,8,F"extensive consultation" with
OL,9,Fbusinesses, with the hopes that a wide-
OL,10,Fencompassing GST reform would "avoid
OL,11,Fthe increased complexity, costs and
OL,12,Fadministrative burden of having
OL,13,Fdifferent rates of GST for different
OL,14,Fgoods".
OL,16,FWhat is included in P&R's tax reform
OL,17,Fpolicy letter?
OL,19,FAlongside these changes, new political
OL,20,Frules hope to legally protect people
OL,21,Ffrom future increases in the GST rate.
