OL,4,Calongside introduction of GST
OL,6,FIf approved, a new requirement would
OL,7,Fmean two-thirds (a 'super majority')
OL,8,Fof the States Assembly would have to
OL,9,Fagree to any fluctuations.
OL,11,FAdditionally, if GST were increased
OL,12,Fbeyond 5%, politicians would be
OL,13,Flegally required to increase
OL,14,Fallowances and benefits.
OL,16,F"We know that one of the biggest fears
OL,17,Ffollowing the introduction of any
OL,18,Fconsumption tax is that it is too easy
OL,19,Ffor governments to just keep
OL,20,Fincreasing it," Deputy Gavin St Pier,
OL,21,FP&R's Vice-President, has stated.
