OL,3,CIncome tax cut proposed in Guernsey
OL,4,Calongside introduction of GST
OL,6,F"We have also given a lot of thought
OL,7,Fto building in protections against
OL,8,Fthis. These include a requirement for
OL,9,Fa host of legal obligations to adjust
OL,10,Fall the other protections for income,
OL,11,Fpensions and benefits in the event of
OL,12,Fany future proposals to increase the
OL,13,Frate."
OL,15,FP&R adds that no final decision will
OL,16,Fbe made on tax reform until the summer.
